data.description: English Cottage and modern design are one located in the sought after Three Rivers community of South Fork Estates offering panoramic views, grounds adorned with native plantings, a seasonal creek, antique street lamps and gardens of picturesque landscape throughout. The residence features an open floorpan with soaring ceilings, custom built ins creating a library space, family room  with a large entertainment center, spacious dining area all open to the chef worthy kitchen featuring granite counters, built in appliances and a noteworthy butlers pantry. The Primary bedroom boasts a sitting area with built ins and French doors leading to the back patio with multiple garden pathways. Additional amenities include stained concrete floors, spacious guest bedroom and bathroom, wood burning stove and multiple French doors and windows allowing an abundance of natural light throughout. A separate guest room not included in the square footage  could be an additional studio, game room or recording studio above the garage and accessed separately from the home. In addition amongst the gardens is an art studio as well as a large 12x24 shed. This property is a must see, call today for your private viewing.
